<p>This chapter covers:</p>
<ul>
  <li>British history starting in the Stone Age</li>
  <li>Starts with arriving populations which affected the languages and religions of Britain</li>
  <li>Following this the development of the Monarchy, church and Parliament</li>
</ul>

